import React from 'react';
import logo from './logo.svg';
import Paragraph from "./components/paragraph";
import Line from "./components/line";
import MyNavbar from './components/nav.js';
import Divider from './components/divider.js';


const Privacy = ( {image, caption, color} ) => {
    return(
        <React.Fragment> 
        <MyNavbar></MyNavbar>

        <Line text = "Last Updated: February 4, 2020 "
        ></Line>

        <Paragraph text = ""
        ></Paragraph>

        <Paragraph text = "Thank you for choosing to be part of our community at Iris (“Company”, “we”, “us”, or “our”). We are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. If you have any questions or concerns about our notice, or our practices with regards to your personal information, please contact us at irissuggestions@gmail.com."
        ></Paragraph>

        <Paragraph text = "This privacy notice applies to all information collected through our mobile application, ('Apps'), and/or any related services, sales, marketing or events (we refer to them collectively in this privacy notice as the 'Services')."
        ></Paragraph>

        <Paragraph text = 'Please read this privacy notice carefully as it will help you make informed decisions about sharing your personal information with us.'
        ></Paragraph>

        <Line text = 'TABLE OF CONTENTS'
        ></Line>

        <Line text = '1. WHAT INFORMATION DO WE COLLECT?'
        ></Line>


        <Line text = '2. WILL YOUR INFORMATION BE SHARED WITH ANYONE?'
        ></Line>


        <Line text = '3. HOW LONG DO WE KEEP YOUR INFORMATION?'
        ></Line>


        <Line text = '4. HOW DO WE KEEP YOUR INFORMATION SAFE?'
        ></Line>


        <Line text = '5. DO WE COLLECT INFORMATION FROM MINORS?'
        ></Line>


        <Line text = '6. WHAT ARE YOUR PRIVACY RIGHTS?'
        ></Line>


        <Line text = '7. CONTROLS FOR DO-NOT-TRACK FEATURES'
        ></Line>


        <Line text = '8. DO CALIFORNIA RESIDENTS HAVE SPECIFIC PRIVACY RIGHTS?'
        ></Line>


        <Line text = '9. DO WE MAKE UPDATES TO THIS POLICY?'
        ></Line>

        <Line text = '10. HOW CAN YOU CONTACT US ABOUT THIS POLICY?'
        ></Line>
        

        





        <Paragraph text = ''
        ></Paragraph>

        </React.Fragment>

    
    )
  }
  
  export default Privacy;
